ation_m = |elevation_ft = |postal_code_type = [[Postal codes in Palau|Postcodes]] |postal_code = |area_code = (+680) 654 |area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Palau|Area code]] |blank_name_sec1 = License plate |blank_info_sec1 = |website = |footnotes = }} '''Melekeok''' ({{IPAc-en|lang|pron|ˈ|m|ɛ|l|ə|ˌ|k|eɪ|ˌ|ɔː|k}})<ref name="MerriamWebster">{{MerriamWebsterDictionary|Melekeok|accessdate=2017-04-04}}</ref> is a town in the [[Melekeok|State of Melekeok]] (one of [[Palau]]'s sixteen [[States of Palau|states]]). It is located on the east coast of Palau's largest island, [[Babeldaob]]. On October 2006, the settlement of [[Ngerulmud]], located {{convert|2|km|abbr=on}} from the village of Melekeok, became the seat of Palau's government, replacing [[Koror City|Koror]].<ref name=BBCtimeline />
==Demographics== According to the 2005 census, 271 people resided in Melekeok town.
