Time in [[Brunei]] is given by '''Brunei Darussalam Time''' ('''BNT''') ([[UTC+08:00]]). Brunei does not currently observe daylight saving time.<ref>http://www.timeanddate.com/time/zone/brunei/bandar-seri-begawan Time zone in Bandar Seri Begawan, Brunei</ref>

